<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" data-tool="perc-rule">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>PERC Rule Calculator | Pulmonary Embolism Rule-Out | PE Low Risk | RxMedCalc</title>
<meta name="description" content="Free PERC rule calculator for pulmonary embolism rule-out in low-risk patients. If all 8 PERC criteria are negative AND pre-test probability is low, PE is safely excluded without D-dimer or imaging. AHA/ESC guidelines."/>
<meta name="keywords" content="PERC rule, PERC calculator, pulmonary embolism rule out, PE rule out criteria, PERC negative PE, D-dimer PE, low risk PE, pulmonary embolism emergency, PERC 8 criteria, PERC vs D-dimer"/>
<meta name="robots" content="index, follow"/>
<link rel="canonical" href="https://rxmedcalc.com/medical-calculators/perc-rule"/>
<meta property="og:title" content="PERC Rule Calculator | PE Rule-Out | RxMedCalc"/>
<meta property="og:description" content="PERC rule for pulmonary embolism rule-out. 8 criteria — if all negative in low pre-test probability, safely excludes PE without D-dimer."/>
<meta property="og:url" content="https://rxmedcalc.com/medical-calculators/perc-rule"/>
<link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" type="image/svg+xml"/>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"/>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin/>
